  "text": "Min/+ mouse was subsequently recognised as a paralog for human familial adenomatous polyposis (FAP) syndrome and provided confirmation of the causal gene mutation in sporadic CRCs with 5q21 deletions [CITATION_1] ; later studies showed that somatic inactivation of APC is observed in >80% of sporadic CRCs [CITATION_2] .",
